msgctxt "an8.61:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8"

#. </p><p>
#. VAR: 7. Bhūmicālavagga → cāpalavaggo (bj) | paṇṇāsakāsaṅgahito dutiyavaggo (s1) | cālavaggo (s2, s3)
msgctxt "an8.61:0.2"
msgid "7. Bhūmicālavagga"
msgstr "7. Earthquakes"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 61. Icchāsutta → lābhicchāsuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an8.61:0.3"
msgid "61. Icchāsutta"
msgstr "61. Desire"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.294"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an8.61:1.1"
msgid "“Aṭṭhime, bhikkhave, puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are eight kinds of people found in the world."

msgctxt "an8.61:1.2"
msgid "Katame aṭṭha?"
msgstr "What eight?"

msgctxt "an8.61:1.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno pavivittassa viharato nirāyattavuttino icchā "
"uppajjati lābhāya."
msgstr ""
"First, when a mendicant stays secluded, living independently, a desire "
"arises for material possessions."

msgctxt "an8.61:1.4"
msgid "So uṭṭhahati ghaṭati vāyamati lābhāya."
msgstr "They try hard, strive, and make an effort to get them."

msgctxt "an8.61:1.5"
msgid "Tassa uṭṭhahato ghaṭato vāyamato lābhāya lābho nuppajjati."
msgstr "But material possessions don’t come to them."

msgctxt "an8.61:1.6"
msgid ""
"So tena alābhena socati kilamati paridevati, urattāḷiṃ kandati, sammohaṃ "
"āpajjati."
msgstr ""
"And so they sorrow and pine and lament, beating their breast and falling "
"into confusion because they don’t get those material possessions."

msgctxt "an8.61:1.7"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave:"
msgstr "This is called"

msgctxt "an8.61:1.8"
msgid ""
"‘bhikkhu iccho viharati lābhāya, uṭṭhahati ghaṭati vāyamati lābhāya, na ca "
"lābhī, socī ca paridevī ca, cuto ca saddhammā’. (1)"
msgstr ""
"a mendicant who lives desiring material possessions. They try hard, strive, "
"and make an effort to get them. But when possessions don’t come to them, "
"they sorrow and lament. They’ve fallen from the true teaching."

#. </p><p>
